{"title":"about","date":"2019-03-02T15:34:38.000Z","updated":"2019-03-03T03:27:14.640Z","content":"<div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"./image/1.jpeg\" alt=\"space\" data-zoomable><br><img src=\"./image/2.jpeg\" alt=\"space\" data-zoomable><br><img src=\"./image/3.jpeg\" alt=\"space\" data-zoomable><br><img src=\"./image/4.jpeg\" alt=\"space\" data-zoomable><br><img src=\"./image/5.jpeg\" alt=\"space\" data-zoomable><br><img src=\"./image/6.jpeg\" alt=\"space\" data-zoomable></p></div>\n<p>如果生命有意义，那么它的意义就是当下，就是一个片刻接一个片刻你握在手头上的这些时间，往往我们追寻答案的时候，沿途荆棘遍地，但穷尽宇宙的jin</p>\n<p>我们最贪恋的过往，以及我们总是急着奔向的未来，并不比一场梦更真实；当周遭的声音总是在说“快点，再快点”，你还是可以停下来，去看看就在眼前的真相。</p>\n<h2 id=\"生命只在这一瞬间，\"><strong>生命只在这一瞬间，</strong><a href=\"about#生命只在这一瞬间，\"></a></h2><p>Life is just a Moment…….</p>\n<h2 id=\"活在当下，\"><strong>活在当下，</strong><a href=\"about#活在当下，\"></a></h2><p>LIVE IT.</p>\n<h2 id=\"爱在当下，\"><strong>爱在当下，</strong><a href=\"about#爱在当下，\"></a></h2><p>LOVE IT.</p>\n<h2 id=\"享受当下。\"><strong>享受当下。</strong><a href=\"about#享受当下。\"></a></h2><p>ENJOY IT.</p>\n<p>···</p>\n","slug":"about","link":"https://i542873057.github.io/about/","toc":[{"title":"","id":"生命只在这一瞬间，","index":"1"},{"title":"","id":"活在当下，","index":"2"},{"title":"","id":"爱在当下，","index":"3"},{"title":"","id":"享受当下。","index":"4"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Jianan Shao","license":"邵佳楠的个人博客","published":"2019年3月2日","link":"<a href=\"https://i542873057.github.io/about/\" title=\"about\">https://i542873057.github.io/about/</a>"}}